      "name": "BrgyLink",
      "shortDescription": "A simple information and service portal designed for barangays, built using Bootstrap 5 and ASP.NET Core Razor Pages with C#. The project provides a user-friendly interface for barangay management and services.",
      "description": "The Barangay Information & Service Portal is a responsive web-based system designed to simplify barangay operations and improve access to public services. It is built with ASP.NET Core Razor Pages, C#, Bootstrap 5, and a secure role-based access structure.\n\nKey Features:\n\n• Resident Management — Maintain resident profiles, personal information, household details, and residency status.\n\n• Document Services — Process applications for barangay clearances, certificates of residency, and other official documents.\n\n• Blotter Management — Record, monitor, and manage reported incidents for improved public safety and case tracking.\n\n• Payment System — Accept and monitor service payments through GCash and other supported payment methods.\n\n• Reports — Generate reports for resident records, incidents, document requests, and financial transactions.\n\n• AI FAQ Chatbot — Provide residents with automated answers to frequently asked questions at any time.\n\n• User Access Control — Secure sensitive information using roles and permissions for administrators, barangay officials, staff, and residents.\n\n• Announcements — Publish important news, schedules, emergency notices, and community updates.\n\n• Searchable Records — Locate residents, documents, incidents, and transactions using multiple search criteria.\n\n• Responsive Design — Provide a user-friendly experience across desktop computers, tablets, and mobile devices.",
